title: Asset Listing: List $BNT on ETH v1
body:
Intro: This is a vote to list $BNT on C.R.E.A.M. ETH v1 market -- with a collateral factor of 40% and collateral cap off.

Proposal: By @glenn on June 20, 2021 -- https://forum.cream.finance/t/proposal-add-bancor-network-token-bnt-as-collateral-asset-with-60-collateral-factor/1777

Rational: $BNT has very strong liquidity, community engagement, and is not yet listed on any lending market.

For:  
Add Bancor Network Token (BNT) as a collateral asset with Collateral Factor: 40% and Collateral Cap: Off

Against:  
Do not list Bancor Network Token (BNT) as a collateral asset
author: 0x81f8CaBe89066d43EB4faFD8E4E5256C102E6E30
